{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","Contact the DVLA"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/contact-the-dvla.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/contact-the-dvla"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"2380","business_proposition":false,"alternative_title":"Find the right number, email or postal address to contact the DVLA","overview":"Find the right number, email or address to contact the DVLA about driving licences, vehicle tax, vehicle registration","updated_at":"2012-10-03T12:11:15+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>There are different contact details for the <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> depending on your enquiry.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>Check the <a href=\"/browse/driving\" title=\"Driving on GOV.UK\">driving section</a> first to see if your question is answered there.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>General information</h2>\n\n<p>You can use the following information or the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://emaildvla.direct.gov.uk/emaildvla/cegemail/dvla/en/index.html\" title=\"Contact the DVLA\">use the online service</a> to contact the <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Driver Licensing Enquiries</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Telephone:</strong> 0300 790 6801 <br />\n<strong>Textphone:</strong> 0300 123 1278 <br />\n<strong>Fax:</strong> 0300 123 0784 <br />\n<strong>Fax from outside the UK:</strong> +44 (0)1792 786 369<br />\nMonday to Friday 8am to 7pm<br />\nSaturday 8am to 2pm</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\nDrivers Customer Services\n<br />Correspondence Team\n<br /><abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>\n<br />Swansea\n<br />SA6 7JL\n<br />\n</p></div></div>\n\n<h2>Driver Check Service</h2>\n\n<p>Hire car companies can contact the <strong>Driver Check Service</strong> to check the licence of someone hiring a car. The driver must give their permission for the check.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Driver Check Service</strong>  </p>\n\n<p>09061 393 837<br />\nCalls charged at 49p a minute</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Driving and medical issues</h2>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Drivers Medical Enquiries</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Telephone:</strong> 0300 790 6806 (car or motorcycle), 0300 790 6807 (bus, coach or lorry)<br />\n<strong>Fax:</strong> 0845 850 0095<br />\nMonday to Friday 8am to 5:30pm<br />\nSaturday 8am to 1:00pm</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\nDrivers Medical Enquiries\n<br /><abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>\n<br />Swansea\n<br />SA99 1TU\n<br />\n</p></div></div>\n\n<h2>Registration and tax</h2>\n\n<p>You can use the following information or the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://emaildvla.direct.gov.uk/emaildvla/cegemail/dvla/en/index.html\" title=\"Contact the DVLA\">use the online service</a> to contact the <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Vehicle Registration and Tax enquiries</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Telephone:</strong> 0300 790 6802<br />\n<strong>Text phone:</strong> 0300 123 1279<br />\n<strong>Fax:</strong> 0300 123 0798<br />\nMonday to Friday 8am to 7pm<br />\nSaturday 8am to 2pm</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\nVehicle Customer Services\n<br /><abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>\n<br />Swansea\n<br />SA99 1AR\n<br />\n</p></div></div>\n\n<h2><abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> local offices</h2>\n\n<p>You can also contact your <a href=\"/dvla-offices\" title=\"Find your nearest DVLA office\">nearest <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> local office</a>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p><abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> local offices and the contact centre are closed on <a href=\"/bank-holidays\" title=\"Public holidays\">public holidays</a>.</p>\n</div>\n\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Driving licences","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/driving%2Fdriving-licences.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes getting a driving licence, fees and tracking your application","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=driving%2Fdriving-licences","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving/driving-licences"},"parent":{"title":"Driving","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/driving.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Book your driving test or get a tax disc online, find out the legal requirements for buying, owning, importing or scrapping a car or motorcycle, and read about your rights and responsibilities as a driver.","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=driving","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving"},"parent":null}}]],["related",[{"title":"Change the address on your driving licence","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/change-address-driving-licence.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/change-address-driving-licence","format":"transaction","details":{"need_id":"847","business_proposition":false}},{"title":"Change your name and address on your vehicle registration certificate (V5C)","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/change-name-address-on-vehicle-registration-certificate-v5c.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/change-name-address-on-vehicle-registration-certificate-v5c","format":"answer","details":{"need_id":"1884","business_proposition":false}},{"title":"Change the photo on your driving licence","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/change-photo-driving-licence.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/change-photo-driving-licence","format":"trans